                     <interp inst="t18291029-117-off651" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-117-cd652" type="crimeDate">20th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-117-off651 t18291029-117-cd652"></join>, 3 live tame fowls, price 4s. 6d., the property of 
                     
